summary: This document is a Revolving Credit and Guaranty Agreement dated November 17, 2025, involving Compass, Inc. as the borrower, various lenders and issuing banks, and Morgan Stanley Senior Funding, Inc. as the administrative and collateral agent. It outlines the terms for loans and letters of credit, representations and warranties, conditions for borrowing, covenants, financial covenants, guaranty provisions, events of default, and miscellaneous provisions including governing law and notices.
